description: Have you been looking for that ideal home, one that seamlessly blends new with traditional, one that is perfectly located so that you can walk to everything there is in the neighborhood, and one that you can move in and enjoy right away?  This could be your home!  This perfectly sized home offers great sized rooms, wonderful light, and newer kitchen and bathrooms, yet retains the feel of history in its wood details and multi level living.  Note the interesting and stylish kitchen, the relaxing baths both adding visual appeal, while the oversized living room, the bedrooms on a different floor, and even the oversized closets make your day to day enjoyable.  If you are ready to start a terrific life in South Boston, then come see this beautiful home! Open House cancelled, please reach agent for showings
